<text top="2981" left="149" width="967" height="35" font="font17" id="p1_t68" reading_order_no="125" segment_no="13" tag_type="footnote">This  information  is  based  on  a  comprehensive  review  we  conducted  in  February  2004</text>
<text top="3018" left="148" width="415" height="31" font="font18" id="p1_t69" reading_order_no="126" segment_no="13" tag_type="footnote">and  revisited  in  September  2005  [8].</text>
<text top="699" left="1170" width="974" height="63" font="font3" id="p1_t70" reading_order_no="48" segment_no="1" tag_type="text">reveals  an  ambiguous  picture.  On  one  hand,  all  the</text>
<text top="751" left="1168" width="977" height="63" font="font3" id="p1_t71" reading_order_no="49" segment_no="1" tag_type="text">vendors  acknowledge  the  importance  of metadata  and</text>
